Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.03,0:02:10.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,环…境省？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.56,0:02:16.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  环境省超自然灾害对策室
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.59,0:02:20.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,简单来说就是消除恶灵的国家机关
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.99,0:02:22.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,神乐！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.06,0:02:25.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,黄泉
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.98,0:02:27.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,黄泉！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.31,0:02:35.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,黄泉  黄泉…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.69,0:02:39.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,土宫！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.24,0:02:41.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小千
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.32,0:02:43.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是怎么回事  土宫！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.70,0:02:50.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,头次斩杀的类型D居然是熟人
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.35,0:02:52.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有点挨不住啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.17,0:02:58.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且并非低等怨灵  而是被魍魉操控的死者的肉体
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.72,0:02:59.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.20,0:03:03.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,超自然灾害源的活动已经平定
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.80,0:03:06.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,各地的灵气压也恢复到了正常值
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.51,0:03:08.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个特异点呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.30,0:03:16.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,于1950时荒川河岸附近的出现之后反应就消失了 
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.82,0:03:17.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真让人在意
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.57,0:03:21.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让处理班恢复到通常待机状态吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.70,0:03:24.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,观测班继续警戒
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.09,0:03:24.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.99,0:03:25.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.22,0:03:30.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让神乐先休息一下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.35,0:03:31.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.52,0:03:34.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在精神不稳定的情况下进行作战的话
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.54,0:03:38.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很容易引发失误  更可能会让同伴陷入危险的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.50,0:03:40.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这话真冷谈
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.15,0:03:43.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果措辞委婉能让事态好转的话
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.87,0:03:45.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你有让事态回转的好办法吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.92,0:03:48.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让谏山黄泉也一同休假如何
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.38,0:03:54.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让土宫神乐觉得只有自己被排挤在任务之外会起到反效果
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.24,0:03:56.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果是她的话相信也能安定神乐的精神状态
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.68,0:03:58.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.56,0:03:59.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.36,0:04:03.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没什么  小桐你冷谈的说法也挺不错的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.64,0:04:04.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.29,0:04:12.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,代替前几日在交通事故中去世的保健医生中林老师
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.23,0:04:16.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,新的板桥老师上任了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.79,0:04:20.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放学后保健委员好像还有个会议
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.96,0:04:23.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真锅  你听见了吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.01,0:04:24.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.12,0:04:26.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别忘了出席
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.41,0:04:31.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,兄长  你找我有什么事
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.39,0:04:36.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,实际上是把家主传给黄泉的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.74,0:04:38.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想提前预定
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.95,0:04:41.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,兄长…难道
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.27,0:04:44.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用那么担心
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.63,0:04:46.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,暂时还死不了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.93,0:04:50.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但话说回来  这年纪了谁也不知道以后会出什么事
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.10,0:04:55.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以想在还能动弹的时候让她继承家主  我也好安心
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.56,0:04:56.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来如此
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.05,0:05:04.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我打算在下次的分家会议上  正式把家主之位传给黄泉
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.94,0:05:08.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幽  希望你能帮我准备一下此事
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.77,0:05:09.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.56,0:05:11.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.66,0:05:13.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冥
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.45,0:05:14.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.39,0:05:18.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正如你听到的  帮我准备吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.87,0:05:20.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.48,0:05:25.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,高桥
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.90,0:05:26.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,田宮
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.23,0:05:27.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,津村 
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.58,0:05:29.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,土宮
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.05,0:05:31.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,土宮今天也请假吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.05,0:06:29.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀  欢迎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.24,0:06:33.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.99,0:06:35.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  没事
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.79,0:06:40.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是新来的板桥
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.69,0:06:41.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请多指教
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.10,0:06:43.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.25,0:06:45.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的腿怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.16,0:06:48.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个  以前…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.03,0:06:49.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被玻璃划破的…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.80,0:06:52.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.66,0:06:55.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,坐那边吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.91,0:06:56.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.56,0:07:00.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让玻璃划破的  怎么弄的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.07,0:07:03.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我打碎了窗户
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.53,0:07:04.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真危险
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.46,0:07:15.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已经好得差不多了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.53,0:07:17.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样就不会留下伤痕了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.90,0:07:21.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要小心一点  你是女孩子嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.80,0:07:23.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.69,0:07:26.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了  包扎完毕
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.64,0:07:28.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.21,0:07:31.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果感到绷带有什么不适随时过来
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.49,0:07:33.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我会马上帮你换的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.42,0:07:39.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  对不起  弄疼你了？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.62,0:07:42.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  不是的…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.52,0:07:49.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起…对不起…对不起…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.18,0:07:54.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起…对不起…对不起…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.70,0:08:00.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起…对不起…对不起…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.39,0:08:25.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老师…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.46,0:08:30.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你哭什么
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.50,0:08:34.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明是你杀的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.47,0:08:35.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小千
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.21,0:08:37.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明是你杀的  你又哭什么
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.14,0:08:41.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说点什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.13,0:08:47.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是你干的吧  说话啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.50,0:08:48.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小千
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.64,0:08:51.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还是说连我都要砍吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.50,0:08:53.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别说了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.57,0:08:54.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,会砍的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.75,0:08:57.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管是我还是真红都会砍的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.10,0:08:58.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要再说了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.55,0:08:59.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我那么喜欢你们！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.44,0:09:04.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老师也是  土宫也是  明明很喜欢的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.29,0:09:07.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么会变成这样
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.17,0:09:11.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你说话啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.70,0:09:14.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别一声不吭  就算是借口也行倒是说些什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.99,0:09:20.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我叫你说话你听没听见吗！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.80,0:09:21.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小千
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.07,0:09:25.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你要打…就打吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.25,0:09:30.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恨我的话  随你怎么打都行
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.36,0:09:37.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不应该这样子的…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.34,0:09:42.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算是工作  就算我不想砍…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.06,0:09:44.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算那是我想保护的人…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.26,0:09:46.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么会这样！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.13,0:09:51.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,土宫…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.25,0:09:54.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我错了吧…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.41,0:09:58.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定是我错了…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.16,0:10:02.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以  你们怨我好了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.34,0:10:07.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,揍我好了…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.72,0:10:10.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,求你们了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.33,0:10:17.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你个笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.81,0:10:19.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小千
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.29,0:10:32.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.92,0:10:34.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,黄泉啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.03,0:10:37.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,叔叔  冥姐  你们好
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.12,0:10:39.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来找爸爸吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.40,0:10:41.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  事情已经谈完了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.14,0:10:45.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你最近挺活跃的嘛  黄泉
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.17,0:10:47.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没那种事啦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.26,0:10:50.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说什么呢  狮子丸可是在你手里
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.39,0:10:53.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果不做出点成绩来可不行
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.65,0:11:00.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谏山家代代相传的宝刀  原本可不是你等外道能够使用的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.04,0:11:04.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你要谨记这其中的含义
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.39,0:11:04.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.58,0:11:13.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了  黄泉
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.26,0:11:15.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  没事
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.18,0:11:17.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,保重
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.54,0:11:26.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没错  土宫就是退魔师一族
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.15,0:11:32.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我总有一天也要成为独当一面的退魔师而继承灵兽才行
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.06,0:11:38.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,白叡  那是土宫家相传的最强灵兽
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.31,0:11:43.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要维持那个封印  将灵魂与其相连
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.40,0:11:46.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这就是生为土宫家人的宿命
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.99,0:11:52.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道说土宫经常请假  看到短信就早退是…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.71,0:11:56.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对  这是生为土宫家人的工作
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.40,0:11:57.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这太奇怪了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.38,0:12:00.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太不可思议了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.78,0:12:03.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟然有家人会让小孩子去做那种危险的工作
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.61,0:12:06.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为这是家传的使命…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.06,0:12:08.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那更奇怪
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.49,0:12:11.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么就非要土宫来继承啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.22,0:12:15.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为…就是这种宿命…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.84,0:12:17.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这就奇怪到天边去了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.20,0:12:19.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说使命啊宿命啊什么的太蠢了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.62,0:12:20.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蠢…？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.56,0:12:27.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是说土宫你一定要做的话我也不会反对…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.81,0:12:31.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定要做么…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.76,0:12:33.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可那是…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.57,0:12:39.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.66,0:12:42.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 没什么
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.42,0:12:47.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过  土宫你是真想继承那样的工作吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.80,0:12:50.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.19,0:13:02.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,室长
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.42,0:13:04.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀  小桐
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.56,0:13:06.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你看这个
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.21,0:13:10.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,灵力分布观测班传来的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.52,0:13:12.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说是那个特异点又出现了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.15,0:13:15.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这…特异点有两个
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.33,0:13:20.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大的那个比起以前灵力场规模有所缩小
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.77,0:13:23.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是说分裂了？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.92,0:13:25.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的  的确有这可能
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.42,0:13:55.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,漂亮
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.77,0:13:58.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是不合格
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.69,0:14:02.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,实战的话你可就死了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.62,0:14:04.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,同归于尽也是输
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.16,0:14:06.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要想什么舍身战法
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.91,0:14:10.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想想无伤退敌的方法吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.44,0:14:11.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.60,0:14:13.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过  进步挺大的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.77,0:14:17.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我学会刚才那招反击方式可是花了不少时间的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.38,0:14:20.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,黄泉
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.55,0:14:24.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…这样继续下去真的好吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.32,0:14:26.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,神乐
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.99,0:14:28.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我很怕
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.75,0:14:34.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,开始我并不太明白工作是怎么一回事
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.65,0:14:37.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为看到黄泉驱使灵兽而很羡慕
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.71,0:14:43.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,觉得退治恶灵保护大家是件很帅的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.64,0:14:45.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.04,0:14:47.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.10,0:14:50.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不知道…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.55,0:14:51.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,神乐
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.56,0:14:53.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.83,0:14:55.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要怎么办才好
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.19,0:15:00.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唔…  我也不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.40,0:15:03.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你可以努力奋斗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.74,0:15:05.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也可以放弃离开
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.31,0:15:07.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过做决定的人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.32,0:15:09.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,神乐  是你自己
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.71,0:15:12.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你现在就尽情烦恼吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.93,0:15:14.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管别人说什么
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.44,0:15:17.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要最后你找到自己心中的那个答案就够了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.22,0:15:21.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,至少我是这么一路走过来的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.41,0:15:22.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,黄泉
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.33,0:15:27.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管是什么样的答案  只要是神乐你自己决定的话
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.60,0:15:29.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我都站在你这边
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.51,0:15:32.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.17,0:15:35.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一直都站在你这边
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.96,0:15:41.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  小千
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.53,0:15:44.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上次的那个朋友？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.21,0:15:46.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  说她请客让我赶快过去
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.90,0:15:49.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嘛  挺好的朋友嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.54,0:15:51.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看来她理解你了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.44,0:15:53.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一半一半吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.83,0:15:56.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,足够了  好好珍惜
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.60,0:15:57.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一路小心
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.77,0:15:58.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.86,0:16:01.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回头见
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.00,0:16:07.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,纪之？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.11,0:16:18.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,黄泉吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.07,0:16:24.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冥？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.63,0:16:31.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过  也算放心了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.04,0:16:32.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放心什么
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.64,0:16:35.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,神乐变得精神一些了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.03,0:16:40.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还是老样子成天到晚都在说神乐呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.89,0:16:44.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为  她和我很像嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.25,0:16:45.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,像吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.64,0:16:50.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被恶灵杀死家人  背负着退魔师的使命
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.68,0:16:54.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不想让她承受和我一样的痛苦回忆
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.30,0:16:57.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想保护她
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.45,0:16:58.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,黄泉
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.11,0:17:02.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想就这么一直保护着她
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.45,0:17:06.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是…差不多也到头了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.84,0:17:10.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,神乐也许已经用不着我了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.58,0:17:17.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她啊  一瞬间就把我花了数年才掌握的招式学会了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.99,0:17:20.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,过不了多久她就会超过我的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.09,0:17:22.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,素质真不错呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.35,0:17:25.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  是身世好
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.63,0:17:31.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,继承最强灵兽的土宫家的嫡子
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.21,0:17:34.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,退魔师中也算是屈指可数的家族
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.92,0:17:37.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以及与生俱来的才能
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.87,0:17:41.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她有着我如何渴望也得不到的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.87,0:17:43.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,黄泉
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.37,0:17:47.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然而她却在烦恼着是否要继承这些
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.16,0:17:50.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是讽刺
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.91,0:17:54.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你为了继承谏山家业也付出了不少努力
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.89,0:17:58.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已经有了就算在退魔师中也是数一数二的身手
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.13,0:18:00.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,成长到今天被人称作神童的地步
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.27,0:18:05.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算这样  还是有人觉得我并不怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.20,0:18:08.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在没有人可以责难你了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.10,0:18:10.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抬头挺胸走下去就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.74,0:18:12.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,纪之
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.88,0:18:16.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说你坏话的人  我是不会放过的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.96,0:18:19.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说得最多的不是纪之你么
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.68,0:18:22.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪张嘴…说了？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.40,0:18:29.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.69,0:18:32.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,黄泉  我现在和小千她们在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.52,0:18:34.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嘛  还顺利吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.54,0:18:39.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然说是请我  但输了扑克牌变成我请她们啦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.16,0:18:39.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样么
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.90,0:18:42.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说来黄泉  今天晚饭准备如何
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.11,0:18:44.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.49,0:18:46.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今晚我来做吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.37,0:18:48.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.17,0:18:48.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.75,0:18:49.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没问题？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.03,0:18:51.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,觉得应该没问题的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.73,0:18:53.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想吃什么
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.73,0:18:55.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就吃神乐喜欢吃的东西吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.80,0:18:57.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,黄泉你决定啦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.31,0:18:58.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样的话…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.65,0:19:02.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我想吃蔬菜咖喱汪…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.76,0:19:05.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道了  那回头见
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.70,0:19:11.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,神乐
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.90,0:19:14.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,久等咯
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.12,0:19:15.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,甜点冰淇凌哦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.74,0:19:20.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都没吃吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.08,0:19:22.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,神乐你难道不饿吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.57,0:19:28.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉  我忘记正在进行少量减肥了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.01,0:19:29.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们吃吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.83,0:19:31.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,疼！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.63,0:19:33.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别用边角砸我啦  边角
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.55,0:19:35.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下次再敢这样小心我咬掉你的舌头
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.70,0:19:38.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样好么
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.28,0:19:43.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反正今天的任务已经结束了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.33,0:19:57.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.84,0:20:00.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我回来咯～
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.29,0:20:04.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天吃咖喱哦～
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.12,0:20:21.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,黄泉
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.06,0:20:24.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,叔叔
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.45,0:20:29.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我回来了  叔叔
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.46,0:20:34.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,叔叔？叔叔！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.34,0:21:00.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉  回来晚了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.20,0:21:03.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,神乐你怎么待在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.85,0:21:04.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,黄泉
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.75,0:21:06.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  怎么了？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.81,0:21:09.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,叔叔他…叔叔他…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.09,0:21:17.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,叔叔！这是？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.13,0:21:20.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,黄泉  这时候你跑到哪里玩去了！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.32,0:21:23.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,根本联络不到  一直在找你！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.93,0:21:26.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冥
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.71,0:21:31.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,黄泉  首先请和令尊道别
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.25,0:22:26.36,OP日文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}いつか誓ったのよ　自分の心へと
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.85,0:22:37.04,OP日文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,800)}嘆きの渦にのまれた　君を助けたいと
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.21,0:22:47.76,OP日文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}重ねる時は変えてゆく　理の歯車が銹びたら
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.85,0:22:52.75,OP日文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,800)}もう戻れない　I hate this world
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.98,0:23:00.35,OP日文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,800)}全て壊したい　どこにもまだ行けない
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.51,0:23:03.75,OP日文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}思い出の為に
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.80,0:23:11.02,OP日文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}幸せだったと　あの頃だけ抱きしめ
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.14,0:23:26.51,OP日文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,2000)}遠ざかる夢の足音　胸に刻み込んだ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.25,0:22:26.36,OP中文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}曾经对自己的心灵　许下了誓言
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.85,0:22:37.04,OP中文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,800)}想要救赎　卷入叹息漩涡中的你
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.21,0:22:47.76,OP中文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}交错的时光转瞬即逝　道理的齿轮锈迹斑斓
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.85,0:22:52.75,OP中文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,800)}已经无法后退　我憎恨此世
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.98,0:23:00.35,OP中文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,800)}想要摧毁一切　亦无容身之地
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.51,0:23:03.75,OP中文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}为了思念
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.80,0:23:11.02,OP中文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}将那时仅有的幸福　深情拥抱
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.14,0:23:26.51,OP中文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,2000)}将远去的梦的足音　刻骨铭心
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.92,0:23:37.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下一话  喰灵  -零-
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.02,0:23:39.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「复仇之路」


